dsa.datastructures.queue

Class QueueLinkedList

  • java.lang.Object
    • dsa.datastructures.linkedlist.Linked_List
      • dsa.datastructures.queue.QueueLinkedList

  • public class QueueLinkedList
extends Linked_List
    The QueueLinkedList class contains queue operation which uses linked list to store data.

    QueueLinkedList is thread-safe and is implemented for primitive types only.

    Time Complexity(Best) Time Complexity(Average) Time Complexity(Worst)
    Insert(enqueue) Ω(1) θ(n) O(n)
    Delete(dequeue) Ω(1) θ(n) O(n)
    See Also:
    Linked_List

        public java.lang.Object dequeue()
        Removes the least recently added element.

        This method is equivalent to Linked_List.removeAtIndex(long) where index is 0.

        Returns:
        the element which is removed
        Throws:
